if you are facing problem with airflow installation with docker please try to follow <https://faun.pub/apache-airflow-2-0-complete-installation-with-docker-explained-f07aaJoanne49f1e|this> medium article. make sure that you have stopped related containers.
use:
`docker stop $(docker ps -a -q)`
`docker rm $(docker ps -a -q)`
if you want to stop and remove all running containers and don't have a container that you want to keep running.
